Paul Rogers (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Rogers_(actor) 0 Paul Rogers (22 March 1917 – 6 October 2013) was an English actor of film, stage and television. He was the first winner of the BAFTA TV Award Best Actor in 1955 and won a Tony Award Best Actor winner for The Homecoming in 1967.
